quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,265,aur jo log khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye khuloos niyat se apna maal kharch karte hain un ki misaal aik baagh ki si hai jo onche jagah par waqay ho ( jab ) is par meen parre to dugna phal laaye. aur agar meen nah bhi parre to kher phwaar hi sahi aur khuda tumahray kamon ko dekh raha hai
2,266,bhala tum mein koi yeh chahta hai ke is ka khajoron aur angarro ka baagh ho jis mein nehrain beh rahi hon aur is mein is ke liye har qisam ke meway mojood hon aur usay burhapa a pakray aur is ke nanhay nanhay bachay bhi hon. to ( nagahan ) is baagh par aag ka bhara howa bagola chalay aur woh jal kar ( raakh ka dhair ho ) jaye. is terhan khuda tum se apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum socho ( aur samjhoo )
2,267,momino! jo pakeeza aur umdah maal tum kamate hon aur jo cheeze hum tumahray liye zameen se nikaltay hain un mein se ( raah khuda mein ) kharch karo. aur buri aur napak cheeze dainay ka qasad nah karna ke ( agar woh cheeze tumhe di jayen to ) bajuz is ke ke ( letay waqt ) ankhen band karlo un ko kabhi nah lau. aur jaan rakho ke khuda be parwa ( aur ) qabil sataish hai
2,268,( aur dekhna ) shetan ( ka kehna nah maanna woh ) tumhe tang dasti ka khauf dilaata aur be hiyai ke kaam kar ne ko kehta hai. aur khuda tum se apni bakhshish aur rehmat ka wada karta hai. aur khuda barri kashaish wala ( aur ) sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
2,269,woh jis ko chahta hai danai bkhshta hai. aur jis ko danai mili be shak is ko barri Nemat mili. aur nasiyaat to wohi log qubool karte hain jo aqalmand hain
